flowRoot.flowPara: Double agent (2): When activated, swap this agent with any other tile in play.
Militia (5): If at any time you surround an opponent's agent with militia and/or the edge of the board, that player is eliminated (capture goal).
Scientist (8): If at any time you have a straight, unbroken row of five active Scientists (liberation goal), you win.
Ringleader (2): When activated, activate up to two more friendly sleeper agents.
Recruiter (2): When activated, place another sleeper agent on the board.
Diversion (2): When activated, move any agent to an empty space.
Saboteur (1): When activated, kill this agent and all adjacent tiles. Saboteurs count as killed agents.
Informant (2): When activated, flip any agent belonging to any player. Don't activate this agent, even if it is flipped face-up.
Master of disguise (2): When activated, may use the activation ability of one adjacent active agent (any owner). When face up, counts for both the liberation and capture goals.
Police (2): When activated, activate up to two more friendly sleeper agents.
Immigration (2): When activated, return up to two other agents to their owners' hand. Bounced sleeper agents are not revealed.
